title: Steely Dan Plush TV Jazz-Rock Party (2000) DVDrip Re-Rendered
description:
This is a re-rendering of my previous upload to correct blurriness caused by incorrect render of the interlaced original.


Steely Dan Plush TV Jazz-Rock Party (2000) 

Plush TV Jazz-Rock Party is a live performance by Steely Dan at the Sony Studios as part of the "In the Spotlight" PBS series. Released in 2000, it features tracks from their (at the time) unreleased album "Two Against Nature" but also contains additional tracks as well as interviews.

Unfortunately it was shot in 4:3 aspect. However video and audio quality are excellent. DTS 5.1, AC3 5.1, and AC3 stereo.

Bad Sneakers
Janie Runaway
Josie
FM

Black Friday
Babylon Sisters
Kid Charlemagne
Jack of Speed
Peg
What a Shame About Me
Pretzel Logic
